snippet.title: Clawball - Official Reveal Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Become a cat. Play soccer. Here's your look at gameplay and more from Clawball in this trailer for the upcoming VR sports game, featuring 3v3 team-based multiplayer. Clawball is coming soon to the App Lab for Meta Quest.
